1
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

2
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:22,279
{\an8}<i>Darling, I swear
I didn't do all that, okay?</i>

3
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:25,199
{\an8}<i>Why was I so stupid to trust you?</i>

4
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:27,639
{\an8}<i>I gave you my whole life!</i>

5
00:00:27,640 --> 00:00:31,399
{\an8}<i>And you did this behind my back?</i>

6
00:00:31,400 --> 00:00:34,959
{\an8}<i>Be angry all you want.
Let's go to the clinic.</i>

7
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:36,840
{\an8}<i>Divorce me,</i>

8
00:00:37,360 --> 00:00:38,880
{\an8}<i>Thariq Ridzuwan.</i>

9
00:00:41,440 --> 00:00:43,040
{\an8}I'm sorry, treasure.

10
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:57,840
Darling.

11
00:00:58,800 --> 00:00:59,760
Hi, darling.

12
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:04,400
Are you okay? Do you want to drink or eat?

13
00:01:05,160 --> 00:01:06,040
Are you hungry?

14
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,320
Darling?

15
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:15,320
Okay, I'm sorry for asking
so many questions.

16
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:18,280
I know you just woke up, but...

17
00:01:19,720 --> 00:01:21,559
I just want to know

18
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,360
what really happened.

19
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:25,560
Did you meet up with anyone?

20
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,960
Did someone visit?

21
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:34,160
Do you remember anything?

22
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,760
I do.

23
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:49,880
I want you to divorce me.

24
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:54,720
Divorce me.

25
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,640
Ridz.

26
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,240
What happened?

27
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,200
How's Radwa doing?

28
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,960
See you downstairs.

29
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:47,279
Take leave

30
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,840
until Radwa gets well.

31
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:52,920
What is it?

32
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,640
Radwa.

33
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:00,119
She wants me to divorce her.

34
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,240
What?

35
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:03,280
Why?

36
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:06,439
Someone sent a CCTV photo

37
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:08,079
of me carrying Raudhah into the hotel.

38
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,839
Oh my God!

39
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,839
Didn't you say
we were all there at the time?

40
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,399
Do you think she'll believe me?

41
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,440
Did you try explaining?

42
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:18,839
I told her, but she refused to listen!

43
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:23,520
Okay, look. Try to talk to her properly.

44
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:26,920
- But wait for her to cool down.
- It won't make a difference.

45
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:31,599
I made her feel betrayed twice.

46
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,839
First, five years ago,
when I broke it off with her.

47
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:35,480
Now, it's about Raudhah.

48
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:39,399
Ridz, neither of them is your fault
if you think about it.

49
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:41,239
But I'm still the cause.

50
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,960
Then open up everything.

51
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,479
Until she understands you're innocent.

52
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,520
Ridz.

53
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:50,120
Tell her the truth

54
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:53,400
about Raudhah
and what happened five years ago.

55
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:55,120
Okay?

56
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,959
So? Is everything enough?

57
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,559
Yes, Datin.

58
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,639
I'll make sure to settle it tonight.

59
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:25,680
Good.

60
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:27,919
One more thing.

61
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:31,080
You know Thariq
is investigating all this, right?

62
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,840
Be careful. Don't get caught.

63
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:35,680
All right, Datin.

64
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,200
Darling.

65
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,040
How do you feel?

66
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,160
I trusted you.

67
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,840
I trusted you with all my heart.

68
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:58,080
Treasure, what do you mean?

69
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,879
Swear to me.

70
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:03,200
Promise you'll be honest.

71
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:06,280
Okay, I promise. What's the matter?

72
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:08,720
Raudhah.

73
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,719
She said you're the father of her child.

74
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,560
- So do you believe her?
- No!

75
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:19,960
I won't believe it until there's evidence!

76
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,679
You were in that photo!

77
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,600
Clear and obvious!

78
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,200
Answer me, Ridz!

79
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,200
I'm so stupid.

80
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:36,879
Stupid to believe
I'm the only love in your heart.

81
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:39,800
- Darling, I--
- Don't touch me!

82
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:47,280
Can I explain now?

83
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,959
I trusted you.

84
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:56,039
I loved you.
I cared more about you than about myself.

85
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,599
And this is how you repay me?

86
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,920
- Can you listen to what I have to say?
- No!

87
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,320
Divorce me.

88
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,759
- No, right now--
- Divorce me.

89
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:07,959
And take responsibility
for what you did, Ridz.

90
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:09,400
Okay, fine!

91
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:12,959
Fine. That's me in the photo.

92
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:15,040
But I did nothing, Radwa!

93
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:18,519
Get out! Get out now!

94
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:20,319
- Get out!
- Darling, listen.

95
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:22,640
- What else do you want me to believe?
- Listen!

96
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:26,120
Darling, I won't do that to you.

97
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:30,959
Why should we continue with our marriage

98
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:32,999
if we keep hurting each other?

99
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,119
Darling, no.

100
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:38,558
I'm the one who's been hurting you.
You've never hurt me.

101
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:41,400
- Can you not be like this?
- No.

102
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:47,079
- I hurt you when I can't control myself!
- Darling, I...

103
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,319
I understand.

104
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:50,840
I understand, but please trust me.

105
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:54,319
Yes, that's me in that photo.

106
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:57,039
But I was on a mission, okay?

107
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:59,639
I saw Raudhah that night
and she didn't look okay.

108
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:02,240
I didn't do anything. I swear, darling.

109
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:04,920
Please.

110
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,080
This time,

111
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:10,320
let me go.

112
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,800
I'm sorry.

113
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:18,880
Bless the food and drinks
while I was your wife.

114
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:26,440
God won't promise something
stronger than prayers.

115
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:34,880
In fact, God makes prayers
stronger than fate.

116
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:39,400
Give me a week.

117
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,920
I'll prove I'm innocent.

118
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:44,960
I can't wait that long.

119
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:49,080
You only have an hour.

120
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:53,760
If you can't do this within an hour,

121
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:58,240
divorce me.

122
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:11,920
I promise I'll come back

123
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,000
in an hour.

124
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,639
<i>I know my husband.</i>

125
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:04,799
He wouldn't do anything stupid.

126
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:06,640
Get out of my house. Go!

127
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:09,400
I have evidence.

128
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,760
Damn it!

129
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:31,800
Ridz, is everything okay?

130
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:35,559
Thalia, look after Radwa.
I have something to do.

131
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:36,800
Hey.

132
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:40,360
Sorry to hear what happened to your wife.

133
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,320
Let's go and eat.

134
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:45,679
I don't have time.

135
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:47,439
I have to find Zafir now.

136
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,919
I'll follow you.

137
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:50,279
Me too.

138
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:51,439
You don't need to.

139
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:53,519
Come with me to take care of Radwa.

140
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:56,119
It won't take long.
We'll just look for Zafir.

141
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:57,999
It's not about Zafir.

142
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,639
I know when he makes that face,

143
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:02,079
something bad will happen.

144
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:04,639
- Just stay.
- Dear, don't think that way.

145
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:08,399
- I can handle my brother-in-law.
- I don't feel good. Understand?

146
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:10,999
Then you can add some flavors.

147
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:13,600
I don't have time! I only have an hour.

148
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:16,000
Please don't waste my time.

149
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:19,680
Follow me if you want.
Otherwise, stay here.

150
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:35,440
Sorry, darling.
I can't just let the two of them go.

151
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:37,999
Adrean can't stop Thariq alone.

152
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,959
No!

153
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:40,880
You can't.

154
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:46,159
I'll let you know if anything comes up.

155
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:47,560
Don't worry, okay?

156
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:52,640
Still not okay?

157
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:55,080
Hold on.

158
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:59,520
Take this and look after it.

159
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:04,080
I'll take it back when I return.

160
00:13:05,920 --> 00:13:06,760
Okay?

161
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:11,400
Be careful, darling.

162
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:03,840
<i>If you feel you're in danger,
press this button.</i>

163
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:06,800
<i>I'll come.</i>

164
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,919
What's wrong?

165
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:27,479
- It's Fateh.
- What's the matter?

166
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:30,079
He pressed the emergency button
of the watch I gave him.

167
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:31,640
He's already far away.

168
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:35,000
You know you only have
40 minutes to find Zafir, right?

169
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:38,719
Should we send Megat
and Daniel to rescue Fateh?

170
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:40,599
No, we'll...

171
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:42,679
We'll follow this GPS.

172
00:14:42,680 --> 00:14:44,959
You're running out of time, Ridz.

173
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:48,040
If anything happens to Fateh,
Radwa will never forgive me.

174
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:08,120
You lied.

175
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:13,680
You said you'd be back in an hour.

176
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,080
Dear...

177
00:15:35,280 --> 00:15:36,240
Hi.

178
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:51,279
- Come on.
- Ridz.

179
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:53,999
- Be patient. We have to plan first!
- What plan?

180
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:56,959
I only have one hour.
Radwa gave me an hour!

181
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:59,399
Our gear isn't complete. Don't be rash.

182
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:02,000
Be patient, Ridz.
We don't want to harm others.

183
00:16:03,760 --> 00:16:05,120
Hurry up!

184
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:09,960
Hey!

185
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:14,199
Where do you think you're going?

186
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:15,119
Damn it. Fateh.

187
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:17,999
- Ridz! Be patient!
- Let go!

188
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:20,080
Can't you see Fateh?

189
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:26,280
Move it!

190
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,399
- Quickly!
- Help!

191
00:16:30,400 --> 00:16:32,599
Always fighting back!

192
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:33,799
Help!

193
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:35,839
- Get inside!
- No!

194
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:37,280
Be quiet!

195
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:40,680
- No!
- Hurry up!

196
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:43,760
Silence!

197
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:04,640
Let's get out of here!

198
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:09,040
Ridz!

199
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:27,760
Haider!

200
00:17:33,600 --> 00:17:35,360
Oh no!

201
00:17:36,040 --> 00:17:36,880
Haider.

202
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:39,520
Haider!

203
00:17:51,640 --> 00:17:52,480
Here.

204
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:55,560
Thanks.

205
00:18:03,920 --> 00:18:05,680
Do you think I'm selfish?

206
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:10,560
For hoping he's the one
who entered just now.

207
00:18:14,120 --> 00:18:14,960
No.

208
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:20,320
But I'm sure God responded
to your question.

209
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:24,360
What's the answer you see?

210
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:27,280
If it's true,

211
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:29,880
he would've arrived two hours ago.

212
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:31,320
What do you think?

213
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:35,799
Maybe he has a mission.

214
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:38,680
What mission is more important
than your feelings?

215
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:43,360
No, you're not selfish at all, Radwa.

216
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:47,600
There are a lot of soldiers
in this country.

217
00:18:48,600 --> 00:18:52,000
Commandos, police,
the Royal Malaysian Navy.

218
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:56,559
But you, Husniya Radwa,

219
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:59,080
you only have your husband
to take care of you.

220
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:03,080
And he can't even fulfill
his responsibilities.

221
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:12,879
Maybe my request was ridiculous.

222
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:16,000
I was being too emotional.

223
00:19:16,600 --> 00:19:19,040
One hour. That's not enough.

224
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:23,559
Ten minutes is enough to solve a problem

225
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:25,120
if he really tries.

226
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:28,599
But he chose to neglect you.

227
00:19:28,600 --> 00:19:31,080
His responsibilities for the country?

228
00:19:32,120 --> 00:19:33,320
Bullshit.

229
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:39,720
Do you think my decision is right?

230
00:19:42,520 --> 00:19:44,280
To divorce him.

231
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:47,520
Yes.

232
00:19:49,160 --> 00:19:50,000
As it should be.

233
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:08,999
So many problems to handle these kids!

234
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:12,039
- We even got ambushed.
- If the kids are healthy, it's fine...

235
00:20:12,040 --> 00:20:14,479
We could've sold them.

236
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:16,120
Hey!

237
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:25,760
Come.

238
00:20:26,280 --> 00:20:28,280
Hurry.

239
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:30,080
Come on.

240
00:20:32,880 --> 00:20:34,799
- Let's go.
- Help!

241
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:36,080
Help me!

242
00:20:38,080 --> 00:20:40,400
Fateh, come this way.

243
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:51,480
Slowly.

244
00:20:56,760 --> 00:20:57,760
Come.

245
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:08,680
Shut up!

246
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:11,920
Get inside! Follow me.

247
00:21:16,600 --> 00:21:17,680
Get in!

248
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:20,120
Sit down.

249
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:22,800
- Guard them.
- Be silent!

250
00:21:27,520 --> 00:21:28,760
Bastards.

251
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:31,840
All right.

252
00:21:32,760 --> 00:21:33,959
Fateh.

253
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:35,679
Fateh, you wait here.

254
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:38,959
Where are you going? Don't leave me.

255
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:40,879
Fateh. It won't take long.

256
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:43,479
I'm scared.

257
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:45,279
Fateh, dear. Listen.

258
00:21:45,280 --> 00:21:47,399
If a bad man comes here,

259
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:48,639
run.

260
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:50,360
- Okay?
- Okay.

261
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:53,319
I'll come back.

262
00:21:53,320 --> 00:21:55,159
I promise. Okay?

263
00:21:55,160 --> 00:21:57,239
- Okay.
- Wait here.

264
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:59,440
You're a boy. Be strong.

265
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:14,040
Come with me.

266
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,240
Go.

267
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:36,720
Thariq Ridzuwan.

268
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:40,120
We finally met face-to-face.

269
00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:43,200
Say your last words.

270
00:22:44,120 --> 00:22:45,760
Because today

271
00:22:46,360 --> 00:22:48,879
is the last day

272
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:52,160
you'll breathe on this earth.

273
00:23:20,280 --> 00:23:22,720
Fateh, get up. Fateh.

274
00:23:24,280 --> 00:23:26,320
Boys, find the other kids.

275
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:29,680
Megat, find the kids and rescue them.

276
00:23:30,680 --> 00:23:32,199
Kevin, Daniel.

277
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:34,720
Check everywhere
and make sure everything is clear.

278
00:23:37,560 --> 00:23:38,680
Fateh?

279
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,600
Fateh, wake up.

280
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:43,320
The hospital.

281
00:23:55,480 --> 00:23:59,480
Sorry if you're uncomfortable
with what I said earlier.

282
00:24:01,320 --> 00:24:05,720
I didn't mean to instigate you
to divorce Thariq, but...

283
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:08,160
Logically,

284
00:24:09,360 --> 00:24:12,760
your love for Thariq
should've turned into hatred.

285
00:24:15,320 --> 00:24:17,400
The truth hurts, right?

286
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:19,160
Yes.

287
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:22,200
Love is blind.

288
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:26,759
We have to be smart to realize that

289
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:28,760
we're just their backup plan.

290
00:24:31,240 --> 00:24:33,960
But he said he loves me.

291
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:37,960
Do you mean
after he left you five years ago

292
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:40,520
and got engaged to someone else?

293
00:24:41,280 --> 00:24:42,959
But he came back.

294
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:44,200
And?

295
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:47,079
He made your sister pregnant.

296
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:49,400
Radwa, please open your eyes.

297
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:53,320
Are you sure
your husband can change again?

298
00:24:56,040 --> 00:24:59,919
What your husband did
isn't a regular mistake.

299
00:24:59,920 --> 00:25:02,159
But it's the ultimate betrayal

300
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:05,200
of his wife,
who loves him with all her heart.

301
00:25:11,920 --> 00:25:13,559
But I'm scared.

302
00:25:13,560 --> 00:25:15,319
What are you scared of?

303
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:16,280
Of being alone?

304
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:18,640
Nobody to protect you?

305
00:25:20,760 --> 00:25:22,440
I'm here, Radwa.

306
00:25:23,960 --> 00:25:25,959
I can take care of you,

307
00:25:25,960 --> 00:25:27,520
keep you company,

308
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:29,680
and protect you.

309
00:25:32,840 --> 00:25:33,920
Why?

310
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:36,199
Because

311
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:38,160
I believe in fate.

312
00:25:39,360 --> 00:25:42,359
It was fate that made me
rescue you that night.

313
00:25:42,360 --> 00:25:43,920
Not your husband.

314
00:25:45,120 --> 00:25:47,920
Fate made us listen
to each other's problems.

315
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:50,120
And I believe

316
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:54,000
fate has determined
I'm the man who'll protect you.

317
00:26:00,120 --> 00:26:01,560
We just met.

318
00:26:02,960 --> 00:26:07,279
Yes, I understand that you don't know me
and I don't know you.

319
00:26:07,280 --> 00:26:11,559
But I may have fallen in love with you.

320
00:26:11,560 --> 00:26:12,600
Farez.

321
00:26:13,560 --> 00:26:16,800
I won't force you
to fall in love with me, Radwa.

322
00:26:17,600 --> 00:26:20,159
Whatever you feel toward me,

323
00:26:20,160 --> 00:26:22,000
it's your right and I respect it.

324
00:26:23,200 --> 00:26:24,400
But I'll wait.

325
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:29,440
I'll wait for the time
when you fall in love with me.

326
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:32,000
I believe

327
00:26:33,040 --> 00:26:36,840
that fate has determined
that the time will come soon.

328
00:26:39,880 --> 00:26:42,600
I'll wait for you, Husniya Radwa.

329
00:26:43,520 --> 00:26:44,360
I swear.

330
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,920
I'll wait.

331
00:27:22,600 --> 00:27:24,000
Is Haider here?

332
00:27:31,360 --> 00:27:32,640
Keep an eye on Fateh.

333
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:16,960
What are you doing here?

334
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:22,439
See what your stubbornness did?

335
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:24,200
Forgive me, Thalia.

336
00:28:26,360 --> 00:28:28,440
I told you I had a bad feeling!

337
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:32,079
What did you do to him?

338
00:28:32,080 --> 00:28:34,920
You pressured him and told him to decide.

339
00:28:37,400 --> 00:28:39,719
Look at my husband, Ridz!

340
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:41,120
He's in the ICU!

341
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:43,360
It's all because of you!

342
00:28:44,880 --> 00:28:45,960
Thalia.

343
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:48,879
- What?
- I'm sorry.

344
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:49,880
No!

345
00:28:50,600 --> 00:28:53,759
You're selfish!

346
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:57,000
This is my husband, Ridz!

347
00:28:57,960 --> 00:29:01,320
Where is it? You said you'd protect us!

348
00:29:02,120 --> 00:29:03,919
Where is your protection?

349
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:06,640
My Haider, Fateh, and Radwa!

350
00:29:08,280 --> 00:29:12,520
Enough. Get out now! Get out!

351
00:29:24,760 --> 00:29:26,600
Darling, wake up!

352
00:29:28,040 --> 00:29:31,639
Wake up, darling! Wake up!

353
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:33,519
I'm here.

354
00:29:33,520 --> 00:29:35,080
Wake up!

355
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:39,000
Please wake up.

356
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:50,840
I'm sorry, Fateh.

357
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:15,880
Fateh?

358
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:18,600
Similar, isn't it?

359
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:22,560
Now I understand why

360
00:31:23,280 --> 00:31:24,919
you're always at Teduh

361
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:27,560
and treat Fateh like your own brother.

362
00:31:30,360 --> 00:31:34,560
I feel like Raiza is close by
when I'm with Fateh.

363
00:31:50,160 --> 00:31:52,359
So what's the status?

364
00:31:52,360 --> 00:31:55,159
Holy Dragon entered our vicinity.

365
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:57,239
They took all the kids.

366
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:58,399
Fateh?

367
00:31:58,400 --> 00:31:59,760
Fateh as well.

368
00:32:00,360 --> 00:32:02,120
But he's in the hospital now.

369
00:32:03,360 --> 00:32:06,239
I don't care! You must take care of Fateh.

370
00:32:06,240 --> 00:32:08,759
Take him from there, and then sell him.

371
00:32:08,760 --> 00:32:11,440
If it's too difficult, just kill him.

372
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:13,200
Okay, boss.

373
00:32:14,080 --> 00:32:15,520
We can't wait too long.

374
00:32:16,080 --> 00:32:17,520
Don't let that boy talk!

375
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:20,000
Okay, boss.

376
00:32:20,600 --> 00:32:22,360
I can't do it now.

377
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:25,159
He's under strict control.

378
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:27,999
Well, you can't wait until I get caught!

379
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:30,679
If I get caught,
all of you will be hanged.

380
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:31,720
Do you want that?

381
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:35,720
I know who can go in without restriction.

382
00:32:36,960 --> 00:32:38,079
He'll take me inside.

383
00:32:38,080 --> 00:32:40,000
I'll take care of him.

384
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:26,800
<i>See what your stubbornness did?</i>

385
00:33:35,320 --> 00:33:37,039
<i>Look at my husband, Ridz!</i>

386
00:33:37,040 --> 00:33:38,840
<i>He's in the ICU!</i>

387
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:41,280
<i>It's all because of you!</i>

388
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:01,040
Fateh.

389
00:34:12,040 --> 00:34:13,560
Things happen, Ridz.

390
00:34:16,440 --> 00:34:18,120
I'm stupid, aren't I?

391
00:34:19,639 --> 00:34:21,199
You're not, Ridz.

392
00:34:22,120 --> 00:34:24,560
You just love the people
around you too much.

393
00:34:37,080 --> 00:34:38,040
I quit.

394
00:34:41,679 --> 00:34:43,718
I want to resign from the Holy Dragon.

395
00:34:43,719 --> 00:34:44,999
Ridz.

396
00:34:45,000 --> 00:34:46,520
Calm down.

397
00:34:47,560 --> 00:34:49,840
- Don't decide while you're like this.
- No.

398
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:54,199
I've thought it through.

399
00:34:56,280 --> 00:34:58,200
And this is the best for me.

400
00:35:04,680 --> 00:35:06,640
What happened to Haider

401
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:09,239
wasn't your fault, Ridz.

402
00:35:09,240 --> 00:35:11,440
- It's not.
- Then whose fault is it?

403
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:16,160
Whose fault is it
that Haider's in the ICU?

404
00:35:18,680 --> 00:35:21,800
I'm a burden and the cause of all this. I...

405
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:26,080
Let me end all this. Please.

406
00:35:38,680 --> 00:35:40,040
I'm exhausted.

407
00:36:07,240 --> 00:36:08,600
Husniya Radwa.

408
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:11,800
I'm disappointed in you.

409
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:17,480
I don't really care if you have evidence.

410
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:20,999
I was just hoping

411
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:23,880
you'd appear after an hour.

412
00:36:25,120 --> 00:36:27,440
For the sake of our marriage.

413
00:36:29,360 --> 00:36:31,880
But you failed to do even that.

414
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:39,240
I'm sorry.

415
00:36:41,720 --> 00:36:43,240
I've failed.

416
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:47,920
Be honest with me.

417
00:36:49,560 --> 00:36:52,040
You went on a task
with the Holy Dragon, right?

418
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:11,599
I don't want you to choose
between work and me.

419
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:14,120
But once in a while, Thariq Ridzuwan,

420
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:18,360
I want to feel prioritized.

421
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:28,080
I just want

422
00:37:30,520 --> 00:37:33,960
to make you happy with all my heart.

423
00:37:37,080 --> 00:37:39,599
I just want to love you

424
00:37:39,600 --> 00:37:42,000
with all my heart.

425
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:49,240
But I don't understand.

426
00:37:53,560 --> 00:37:56,760
I only gave you pain.

427
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:03,440
Maybe it's written in fate

428
00:38:04,680 --> 00:38:06,440
that Thariq Ridzuwan...

429
00:38:09,600 --> 00:38:12,480
Thariq Ridzuwan can't make
Husniya Radwa happy.

430
00:38:19,520 --> 00:38:23,480
If you truly cannot bear
the pain any longer,

431
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:31,040
I'm willing to let you go.

432
00:38:38,680 --> 00:38:40,000
I'm sorry.

433
00:39:33,520 --> 00:39:35,719
Ridz, where's Fateh?

434
00:39:35,720 --> 00:39:37,720
What happened to him? Is he okay?

435
00:39:38,360 --> 00:39:40,399
He's okay. The doctor said he's okay.

436
00:39:40,400 --> 00:39:41,799
Okay.

437
00:39:41,800 --> 00:39:43,159
Which ward is he in?

438
00:39:43,160 --> 00:39:45,839
I really need to see him.
He must be scared.

439
00:39:45,840 --> 00:39:47,559
- Do you want to see him?
- Yes.

440
00:39:47,560 --> 00:39:48,839
- I'll take you.
- It's okay.

441
00:39:48,840 --> 00:39:51,599
You look tired. You should go home.
I can go by myself.

442
00:39:51,600 --> 00:39:53,280
Datin. No.

443
00:39:54,600 --> 00:39:57,079
No, Fateh is under strict control now.

444
00:39:57,080 --> 00:39:59,159
If you want to see him,
you have to follow me.

445
00:39:59,160 --> 00:40:02,639
Okay. I'm sorry to trouble you.

446
00:40:02,640 --> 00:40:05,320
But I have a bad feeling.
I need to see him.

447
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:08,000
- Let's go.
- Okay.

448
00:40:26,240 --> 00:40:27,680
How are you, brother?

449
00:40:44,480 --> 00:40:46,759
{\an8}<i>I hate having a sissy son like you!</i>

450
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:48,879
{\an8}<i>Why didn't you fight back?</i>

451
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:50,479
{\an8}Dad.

452
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:52,519
{\an8}- Please don't hit me.
- You should've died back then!

453
00:40:52,520 --> 00:40:54,720
{\an8}You have to fight back.

454
00:40:55,640 --> 00:40:58,639
{\an8}<i>It doesn't matter how.
Play dirty or rough.</i>

455
00:40:58,640 --> 00:41:00,640
{\an8}<i>Just do whatever you can.</i>

456
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:03,359
{\an8}As long as you win.

457
00:41:03,360 --> 00:41:04,960
{\an8}Thank you, friend.

458
00:41:05,560 --> 00:41:06,600
{\an8}You're welcome, friend.

459
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:10,679
{\an8}I have the love of my life.
I'll ask her to come to the tournament.

460
00:41:10,680 --> 00:41:12,439
{\an8}- Okay?
- Okay.

461
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:16,520
{\an8}<i>"Please make Husniya Radwa my wife."</i>

462
00:41:17,040 --> 00:41:19,079
{\an8}I pray for that every day.

463
00:41:19,080 --> 00:41:20,720
{\an8}I'm sorry, Husniya.

464
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:24,240
{\an8}Your future fiancé, Thariq Ridzuwan,

465
00:41:25,400 --> 00:41:26,280
{\an8}is dead.

